OL,3,CWoman jailed for attack on 'best
OL,4,Cfriend' later found dead
OL,6,FA Devon woman was beaten by her "best
OL,7,Ffriend" before she died at a house in
OL,8,FDevon, a court has been told.
OL,10,FCheyenne Loder, 32, from Gorwell Road,
OL,11,FBarnstaple admitted inflicting
OL,12,Fgrievous bodily harm on 38-year-old
OL,13,FHayley Adams in November 2023.
OL,15,FShe was sentenced to two and a half
OL,16,Fyears in prison during a hearing at
OL,17,FExeter Crown Court on Friday 19 April.
OL,19,FHayley Adams was found unresponsive at
OL,20,Fa property in Barnstaple on 4 November
OL,21,Flast year and later died at the scene.
