OL,6,FDevon and Cornwall Police were called
OL,7,Fto a report of a woman in cardiac
OL,8,Farrest at a property on Gorwell Road.
OL,10,FOfficers and paramedics found Ms Adams
OL,11,Funresponsive with injuries to her face
OL,12,Fand head.
OL,14,FThe court heard Ms Adams and Loder had
OL,15,Ftaken a mixture of crack cocaine,
OL,16,Famphetamines and alcohol over a period
OL,17,Fof three days.
OL,19,FWhen first interviewed, Loder said
OL,20,Fthat she did not know what had
OL,21,Fhappened.
