OL,4,Cfriend' later found dead
OL,6,FIn a later statement, Loder said she
OL,7,Fhad known Ms Adams for around eight or
OL,8,Fnine years and that they had become
OL,9,Fbest friends.
OL,11,FLoder said: "There was no one closer
OL,12,Fto me. I loved her and would never
OL,13,Fknowingly harm her."
OL,15,FHowever, she would not answer any
OL,16,Fquestions around the circumstances
OL,17,Faround how Ms Adams had sustained her
OL,18,Finjuries.
