OL,6,FJudge Adkin said Ms Adams had been
OL,7,Fsubjected to a "prolonged and
OL,8,Fpersistent assault" and that the only
OL,9,Fexplanation for the ferocity of the
OL,10,Fviolence were the drugs and alcohol
OL,11,Fconsumed by Loder.
OL,13,FHayley's family paid tribute to her,
OL,14,Fsaying she was "the life and soul" of
OL,15,Fthe party and "lit up any room".
OL,17,F"She had a way of making everyone feel
OL,18,Flike the centre of the world and was
OL,19,Fso excited to run into people she
OL,20,Fknew," they said.
