OL,3,CWoman jailed for attack on 'best
OL,4,Cfriend' later found dead
OL,6,F"She came into her own when her
OL,7,Fchildren were born; she was so proud
OL,8,Fto be their mummy. As a family, our
OL,9,Fworld fell apart when we received the
OL,10,Fshocking news that Hayley had passed
OL,11,Faway.
OL,13,F"We have all, as a family, had
OL,14,Fsleepless nights and have worked our
OL,15,Fway through every emotion: anger,
OL,16,Fshock, heartbreak, sorrow and
OL,17,Fconfusion.
