OL,3,CWoman jailed for attack on 'best
OL,4,Cfriend' later found dead
OL,6,F"Hayley will never see her children
OL,7,Fgrow, get married and have children of
OL,8,Ftheir own. More importantly, her three
OL,9,Fbeautiful children will never have
OL,10,Ftheir mummy to share in their
OL,11,Fsuccesses or support them when they
OL,12,Fneed her.
OL,14,F"Towards the end of her life, it was
OL,15,Fclear that Hayley had some struggles,
OL,16,Fbut she was many things: a mum, a
OL,17,Fbeloved daughter, a fun friend, and a
OL,18,Fdisco queen. We will miss her and
OL,19,Fthink of her every day of our lives."
